                "text": "Middle of Act 1:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "The Sleuth starts working toward solving the mystery. While considering suspects who appear to have the motive, means, and opportunity to commit the crime, however, the Sleuth encounters a twist about midway through this section that shows the crime is more complex than initially thought."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Introduce suspects who appear to have the motive, means, and opportunity to commit the crime."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Have the Sleuth question the most likely suspects, one of whom will end up being the perpetrator."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Create a twist that is attention-grabbing and makes it clear to the reader the investigation will not be straightforward."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Build suspense and tension by offering hints that allow the reader to see possibilities yet unknown to the Sleuth."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "Breakdown:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Act 1 makes up the first 25% of the story."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Set the Sleuth on the Path should be from approximately the 10% - 20% mark of the story."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
