                "text": "Middle of Act 3:",
                "bold": true
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "The reader (and other characters) are able to review what is known and consider the possibilities of the case, as the Sleuth reveals the results of their investigation. The crime appears to be impossible to solve, and the Sleuth has been stymied at every approach, largely being led in the wrong direction by misinterpreting clues or faulty conclusions. The Sleuth must use logic to find a new perspective to understand the uncertainties. The reader begins to doubt the Sleuth's ability to solve the mystery."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "bulleted-list",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Logically and clearly lay out the evidence as it is currently understood. "
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Make it clear that the evidence does not add up and that a new approach must be taken."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "What clues has the Sleuth misinterpreted? "
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "What were the Sleuth's faulty conclusions?"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Raise the stakes as all appears lost."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "list-item",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "Consider how this section develops the subplot."
